<br>
45-49's do NOT attend my raids. If they do, they are entitled to all loot except epic loot. If they agree to that, they come and have fun. If they do not wish to come, that is their right and they will be replaced . Most of the time they get mad because I turn them down in favor of the 50+ raiders.<br>
<br>
As to you &quot;guild&quot; raiding mentality, it's not a guild. It's an widely accepted policy, just as higher level's rotation on VS and Trak, Magister and MF's roto on ring wars/N-ToV. It seems that the only people who have a problem with the way it is currently done are:<br>
